fr.gouv.finances.dgfip.xemelios.importers

Class XmlSplitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • fr.gouv.finances.dgfip.xemelios.importers.XmlSplitter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class XmlSplitter
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    This class splits a file according to its "importable element"'s definition. It also calculates special keys, budget and colletivites if it cans. This class is a spin-off from pre-3.0 DefaultImporteur.
    Since:
    3.0
